<p>Welcome, and thanks for thinking about submitting an 'issue' (or bug reports as they're known for some reason).</p>
<p>Please see the [[Contribute]] page if you want to get involved.</p>


<h2>Issue tracker</h2>
Issue tracker can be found here:
<a href="https://github.com/pygame/pygame/issues">https://github.com/pygame/pygame/issues</a>

